com.hybris.cis.api.executor

Class AbstractServiceMethodExecutor<T,R extends ServiceMethodRequest<T>,U extends CisResult,V,W>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hybris.cis.api.executor.AbstractServiceMethodExecutor<T,R,U,V,W>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractSimpleServiceMethodExecutor

    public abstract class AbstractServiceMethodExecutor<T,R extends ServiceMethodRequest<T>,U extends CisResult,V,W>
extends Object
    Abstraction for 3rd party service calls providing a common framework and options to intercept (e.g. for common validation). T is the type of entity (body) of the request R is the type of our generic request for this service call U is the type of our generic response for this service call V is the type of the vendor specific request W is the type of the vendor specific response
